      "description": "Really nice, well-kept car in good overall condition that runs and drives smoothly. It presents well, has clearly been cared for, and offers a great mix of comfort, reliability, and everyday usability. There may be some normal minor wear consistent with age, but overall it\u2019s a solid, appealing vehicle that\u2019s ready to be enjoyed.",
