    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "Exceptional mint-condition example that presents beautifully throughout and should satisfy even a discerning buyer. The paint, trim, glass, and interior all show at a very high level, with the kind of finish, fit, and overall care you hope to find in a top-tier car. It appears complete, well-kept, and ready to enjoy, with only the most minimal signs of age or use. Buyers should expect a standout example that feels special in person and offers the sort of presentation that is difficult to find.",
