      "description": "Classic car with honest vintage appeal and a solid starting point for someone who wants an enjoyable driver or a light project. It presents decently overall, but it\u2019s not a show car and should be expected to have visible wear, age-related flaws, and likely some sorting depending on how far you want to take it. A straightforward, affordable way into classic ownership with plenty of charm.",
